  "description": "Fix Logo Image Loading Issue on Localhost\n\nResolve the issue preventing logo.png from displaying when the application is run in the local development environment.\n\nRequirements:\n- Verify the logo.png file exists in the expected directory\n- Check the file path reference in the code is correct (relative vs absolute paths)\n- Ensure the image import/require statement uses proper syntax for the build tool\n- Verify the logo file is included in the development server's static assets configuration\n- Check for case-sensitivity issues in the filename (logo.png vs Logo.png)\n- Confirm the image is accessible via direct URL in browser (e.g., http://localhost:3000/logo.png)\n- Verify no CORS or content security policy issues blocking the resource\n- Check browser console and network tab for specific error messages\n- Test that the logo loads correctly after the fix\n- Ensure the fix doesn't break the logo in production environment",
